{"tid":1417104,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"而家正苦係度拖，大家繼續掛住撚狗，聽完錄音帶唔行動升級，正中正苦下懷！","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:24:29.000Z","uid":49803,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"61b6305efab06153fb714194e4635e9f5805d381","tid":1417104,"uid":49803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:00:43.000Z","msg":"和理非搞不合作運動又好<br />\n勇武又好<br />\n點都會搞到其他人利益<br />\n正苦就係想拖，拖到慢慢啲人頂唔住退出<br />\n請記得撚狗唔係重點<br />\n趁仲有咁多人可以忍受不便時就快手贏咗場仗<br />\n而唔係搞一日，又話要等民意返黎<br />\n<br />\n聽日唔係當乜事都無發生，如常返工呀嘛<br />\n<strong>如 常</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b47c3342df38b00e383bac2a0f188b022197b1","tid":1417104,"uid":49803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:04:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d25e6ee764b4e9dde51c1c20045e4624a297adf8","tid":1417104,"uid":49803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:06:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"556eb6d60cfa3135d090b22c65e5e73724fb32bf","tid":1417104,"uid":49803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:24:29.000Z","msg":"推"}]}